    "description": "<p class=\"bb_paragraph\" ><span class=\"bb_img_ctn\"><img class=\"bb_img\" src=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/3017120/extras/1bab241b6f6436b490b565e2ba2e861e.avif?t=1750887849\" width=600 height=200 /></span></p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" >在企鹅王国中的有趣点击器与经济模拟。获取稀有收藏，冒险进入危险的地下城，并建立自己的文明！</p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" ><span class=\"bb_img_ctn\"><video class=\"bb_img\" autoplay muted loop playsinline poster=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/3017120/extras/5415b3112b3f69a3a66700763fc669ac.poster.avif?t=1750887849\" width=600 height=338 ><source src=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/3017120/extras/5415b3112b3f69a3a66700763fc669ac.webm?t=1750887849\" type=\"video/webm; codecs=vp9\"><source src=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/3017120/extras/5415b3112b3f69a3a66700763fc669ac.mp4?t=1750887849\" type=\"video/mp4\"></video></span> </p><h2 class=\"bb_tag\" >游戏中等待你的内容：</h2><ul class=\"bb_ul\"><li><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" > 点击以获取物品 </p></li><li><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" > 收集有价值的收藏 </p></li><li><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" > 探索当前的经济趋势</p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" ><span class=\"bb_img_ctn\"><video class=\"bb_img\" autoplay muted loop playsinline poster=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/3017120/extras/db6f7548d3e4e6920de7fd24dfe5a37f.poster.avif?t=1750887849\" width=600 height=338 ><source src=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/3017120/extras/db6f7548d3e4e6920de7fd24dfe5a37f.webm?t=1750887849\" type=\"video/webm; codecs=vp9\"><source src=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/3017120/extras/db6f7548d3e4e6920de7fd24dfe5a37f.mp4?t=1750887849\" type=\"video/mp4\"></video></span> </p></li></ul><h2 class=\"bb_tag\" >游戏中等待你的内容：</h2><ul class=\"bb_ul\"><li><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" > 平衡的经济模型</p></li><li><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" > 可在后台运行的游戏</p></li><li><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" > 内置的防破解和防作弊保护</p></li><li><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" > 带有主动故事情节的事件</p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" ><span class=\"bb_img_ctn\"><video class=\"bb_img\" autoplay muted loop playsinline poster=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/3017120/extras/8c9e178c142611fde22dfbeb29852b90.poster.avif?t=1750887849\" width=600 height=338 ><source src=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/3017120/extras/8c9e178c142611fde22dfbeb29852b90.webm?t=1750887849\" type=\"video/webm; codecs=vp9\"><source src=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/3017120/extras/8c9e178c142611fde22dfbeb29852b90.mp4?t=1750887849\" type=\"video/mp4\"></video></span></p></li></ul>",
